#. module: equity
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:equity.portal_ubo_form
msgid ""
"Beneficial owners are natural person(s) who ultimately own(s) or control(s) the customer or the natural person(s)\n"
"                    for whose account or on whose behalf a transaction is being conducted or a business relationship is established. It\n"
"                    includes those natural persons that do not have a controlling holding in the company or a formal mandate of any kind\n"
"                    but who are de facto exercising similar control over the company."
